    "title": "Junior Business Development Manager at HUDCO Holdings Services",
    "description": "We at HUDCO Holdings Services are looking for an experienced Business Development Manager based out of Faridabad. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout HUDCO Holdings Services:\nHUDCO Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Client Relationship Management\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in GIS Tools\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Faridabad, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with HUDCO Holdings Services!",
